title: He Is Never Satisfied
itunes:title: He Is Never Satisfied
description:
I really don't know what to do. I need a man's perspective on this issue. I'm 34 and I've been happily married for almost five years. We have no children my husband and I are very much in love. Most of our friends idolize our relationship. People say we look like we're in love. The problem is that he is not satisfied with me sexually. We do it four to six times a week all the time.
